data.description: Charming 3 Bedroom Brick Home Nestled in Desireable Lomax. The Beautifully Renovated Interior Showcases Modern Elegance and Functionality.  With Sleek Countertops, Contemporary Cabinetry & Appliances. Whether you are Cooking up a Feast or Enjoying a Relaxing Soak, These Updated Spaces Offer a Modern Retreat within the Comfort of Your Own Home. Experience Peace of Mind with the Upgraded Pex Piping and HVAC System, Promising Efficiency and Reliability for Years to Come.  From the Floor to Ceiling, Every Aspect of this Home Has Been Thoughtfully Updated to Provide a Fresh and Inviting Ambiance Throughout. Entertain Guests or Simply Unwind in the Serene Outdoor Space Featuring a Covered Patio.  With it's Charming Curb Appeal and Thoughtful Renovations, this Dollhouse is Sure to Steal your Heart! Don't Miss the Opportunity to Make this Delightful Property Yours.  Schedule a Showing Today and Experience the Charm and Comfort of this Lomax Gem Firsthand!
